ng>電影講太陽一爆炸，人類就用機械煞停自轉，造成海嘯，全球馬上殺死一半人，一半人躲到地下基地（故事中地球只餘35億人，是怎決定誰死呢？）。而這麼一場大殘殺的計劃</strong>，到了電影中段飛木星，又幾乎再冚包散一次，我不是太懂這個道德判斷，要再思考一下。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:26:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得反映返佢哋主流觀念，例如佢哋好興話白人以前都滅絕印地安/原住民，宜家我哋慢慢滅絕香港人點解唔得<br />\n<br />\n基本上佢哋同西方尊重人命嘅普世價值差距好遠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855adb1bda5438b22643340fe793dee20494ac11","tid":1041499,"uid":210944,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d98a963fde9bba40a699a95fb8ecfb4cf91d129d","tid":1041499,"uid":63846,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad4856f4729e6b8d7d83bfc4ee13352b27175dcc","tid":1041499,"uid":146063,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:08:29.000Z","msg":"「犧牲小我，完成大我」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:12:17.000Z","msg":"Logic clearly dictates that the needs of the many outweigh the needs of the few."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"Yeah but now clearly China is willing to sacrifice your interest, or the public&rsquo;s interest or even the world&rsquo;s, to suit their own selfish will."},{"pid":"0a8a0fd8e2c9b987bb40357e7fce3df842dce3d2","tid":1041499,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:56:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3526e38b5c3d690f72ed3e756a6ec984ee31968a","tid":1041499,"uid":210944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a8a0fd8e2c9b987bb40357e7fce3df842dce3d2","tid":1041499,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"855adb1bda5438b22643340fe793dee20494ac11","tid":1041499,"uid":210944,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d98a963fde9bba40a699a95fb8ecfb4cf91d129d","tid":1041499,"uid":63846,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:12:17.000Z","msg":"Logic clearly dictates that the needs of the many outweigh the needs of the few."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:53:36.000Z","msg"